26#ifndef _SYS_ZRLOCK_H
27#define _SYS_ZRLOCK_H
28
29#include <sys/zfs_context.h>
30
31#ifdef __cplusplus
32extern "C" {
33#endif
34
35typedef struct zrlock {
36 kmutex_t zr_mtx;
37 volatile int32_t zr_refcount;
38 kcondvar_t zr_cv;
39 uint16_t zr_pad;
40#ifdef ZFS_DEBUG
41 kthread_t *zr_owner;
42 const char *zr_caller;
43#endif
44} zrlock_t;
45
46extern void zrl_init(zrlock_t *);
47extern void zrl_destroy(zrlock_t *);
48#define zrl_add(_z) zrl_add_impl((_z), __func__)
49extern void zrl_add_impl(zrlock_t *, const char *);
50extern void zrl_remove(zrlock_t *);
51extern int zrl_tryenter(zrlock_t *);
52extern void zrl_exit(zrlock_t *);
53extern int zrl_is_zero(zrlock_t *);
54extern int zrl_is_locked(zrlock_t *);
55#ifdef ZFS_DEBUG
56extern kthread_t *zrl_owner(zrlock_t *);
57#endif
58
59#ifdef __cplusplus
60}
61#endif
62
63#endif /* _SYS_ZRLOCK_H */
